name: PERFUME ADVENTURESS 50ml
campo_tres: Take the most luscious, juicy, so-ripe-it’s-about-ready-to-fall-off-the-tree peach and blend it with the warmest, creamiest sandalwood to create an intoxicating concoction that is decadently voluptuous. Delightfully tart citrus eases our way into a satisfyingly sweet peach so vivid that you can almost feel the fuzzy skin. Velvety and warm and languid – the peach, sandalwood and soft musk nuzzle into each other in the most sultry manner. We can’t quite picture getting up out of our chaise lounge with this on, but it is so drop dead glamorous that we assume it will bring the adventure to us. Sensuous and glowing, this makes us purr.

name: PERFUME ALLURING 50ml
campo_tres: A rose in full bloom on a bright summer morning – what could be more beautiful? We don’t know precisely what summer fruits are involved, but to us it smells like berries – sweet, ripe and luscious with a little burst of tartness. There is a delicate and enchanting ylang ylang with a tiny hint of soapiness. And there, at the heart, is a perfect dewy rose, proudly unfurling its glorious petals under the brilliant June sky. This is a rose that is both lush and straightforward. Its unfussy warm simplicity keeps it youthful and fresh. The subtle base notes add a sun-drenched feel and the fruity grace notes evoke the lushness of a summer garden, but never overshadow the lovely evocation of the queen of flowers. Graceful and, as the name promises, completely alluring.

name: PERFUME AL JANA 60ml
campo_tres: An immersion into green naturalness. Aqueous watercolours, Bio-certified materials combined to form a translucent fragrance, characterised by an unprecedented refinement. The notes include thyme, lemon, star anise, helichrysum, ylang ylang, cypress, salvia sclarea, Virginia cedar, vetiver, sandalwood and tonka bean.

name: PERFUME ASMAR OUD 60ml
campo_tres: Dusky scent, of earth and sun, of tanned skin and warm sand. A concentrated but pleasant amber fragrance, strong and delicate thanks to the careful blend of warm notes. A foray into the dreamy heart of a thousand and one nights. When Dorian Grey meets Scheherazade. With bergamot, honey, carnation, coffee, amber cigar, grape marc, amber, tobacoo, chamois, musk and vanilla.

name: PERFUME BURQA OUD 60ml
campo_tres: Like pure blood flowing, mystical and fluid, from every temple, with tones of Chinese ink and bewitched by essences of hard wood, this anthracite fragrance is a liquid incense with a notable prestige and elegance. With notes of jasmine, rose, black violet, cardamom, sage, leather, benzoin, myrrh, black ink, rubber sap, black amber, teck wood, patchouli and guaiac wood
